name: CryptoSerpent #001
description: Phillip Josh Sweet is a 28-year-old former gym assistant who enjoys adult colouring books, social media and worship. He is considerate but can also be very violent and a bit cowardly.   He is addicted to strawberry bonbons. The problem intensified. Phillip has lost two jobs as a result of his addiction, specifically: tea maker and gym assistant.   He is an Egyptian Christian who defines himself as gay. He started studying sports science at college but never finished the course. He is allergic to peanuts.
